8690.html/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4wbddbj20yi22onpd'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4wbddbj20yi22onpd-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4wbddbj20yi22onpd-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4wbddbj20yi22onpd-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4wbddbj20yi22onpd-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678690.html/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4yqi1yj20yi22ox6p'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4yqi1yj20yi22ox6p-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4yqi1yj20yi22ox6p-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4yqi1yj20yi22ox6p-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd4yqi1yj20yi22ox6p-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" /><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678690.html/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd5bodecj20yi22ohdt'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd5bodecj20yi22ohdt-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd5bodecj20yi22ohdt-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd5bodecj20yi22ohdt-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd5bodecj20yi22ohdt-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678690.html/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd53q0wvj20yi22o1ky'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd53q0wvj20yi22o1ky-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd53q0wvj20yi22o1ky-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd53q0wvj20yi22o1ky-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd53q0wvj20yi22o1ky-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><dl class='gallery-item'>\n\t\t\t<dt class='gallery-icon portrait'>\n\t\t\t\t<a href='https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/678690.html/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd56u3raj20yi22ou0x'><img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd56u3raj20yi22ou0x-150x150.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd56u3raj20yi22ou0x-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd56u3raj20yi22ou0x-440x440.jpeg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/03/6fd52fd7ly1h0nd56u3raj20yi22ou0x-50x50.jpeg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 150px) 100vw, 150px\" /></a>\n\t\t\t</dt></dl><br style=\"clear: both\" />\n\t\t</div>\n\n<p><strong>以下为中国数字时代编辑摘自网民评论：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>韩廿：让医护人员歇歇吧！</p>\n<p>JohnnyM6：真的有对《听我说谢谢你》ptsd。</p>\n<p>Leissigen：最会表面功夫形式主义。</p>\n<p>YandexJunk：因为你的尬舞，医务工作者得多站3分钟。</p>\n<p>没有感情的测试杂工：正常，我们这边精神病院也要做核酸检测。</p>\n<p>夜卧_听雨：中国式感动之流量密码。</p>\n<p>是不是静不下来：没有感动，只有感叹，形式主义无所不在。</p>\n<p>每天下午会发呆：大白：我很累 快点吧 。孩子：真尴尬 怎么还没结束。老师：上面要求的，没办法完成任务。</p>\n<p>瓦夫凯123：太墨迹了，磕头吧！安全效率！</p>\n<p>7parks ：&#8221;听我说谢谢你，因为有你，温暖了四季&#8221;，跳舞送祝福的传播速度比冠的传播速度还要快，一时间竟然不知道取悦的是工作的大白，还是屏幕前的用户。</p>\n<p>花木街道刘女士：对不起恶心到了。</p>\n<p>中危研究所：不是洗脚就还行（我底线够不够低）。</p>\n<p>北国佳人李春姬：他们是不是觉得这样很感人？</p>\n<p>Castle-ZYM：形式主义巅峰之作。</p>\n<p>笑笑的小笑：领导用了三秒钟发话，医护人员用三分钟看完，老师们花了30分钟想如何表现，孩子们用了三天排练。很感动，但真没必要，形式大于意义。</p>\n<p>不要桃_走：要说实话吗，好像邪教啊……</p>\n<p>why_do_this：确实是一种精神上的传染病。</p>\n<p>以太香：集權主義美學。</p>\n<p>三顿碧游岛岛子：比新冠更可怕。</p>\n<p>妈宝喵：警惕拜登打跳舞牌！</p>\n<p>funtttt：一线医护大白是真辛苦，这点只要有点人性的人都不会否认，值得尊敬与感谢。但指挥无能，这些大白的辛苦付出，效果会大打折扣，折腾大白，折腾百姓。一将草包，累死三军。</p>\n<p>若华1620：能集合这么多只会作秀的神经病，组织者是哪个？挺有才啊。</p>\n<p>养鸽日记：穿着防护服又热又闷，最好的感谢方式是好好配合，让她们赶紧做完早早下班！！！</p>\n<p>摘花高处du身轻：这份“感谢”送给领导，给大白加工资！来点实在的， 再不济让他们休息下。</p>\n<p>钝钝啪：自我感动之领导爱看。</p>\n<p>植物眼：这个舞已经人传人了？</p>\n<p>桔子水晶11：这个是另一种传染病。</p>\n</blockquote>\n","author":1069,"categories":[18271,43134,41492,38912,38927],"tags":[40917,45235,9540,39920,21038]}